<h4 id="12-brew-cask">1.2 brew cask</h4>
<ol>
  <li>brew cask is an extension to brew that allows management of graphical
applications through the Cask project.</li>
  <li>Cask offers a way to command line manage the installation of graphical
applications.</li>
</ol>

<h3 id="2-ruby">2 Ruby</h3>
<p>ruby使用rvm即Ruby Version Manager来升级Ruby</p>
<h4 id="rvm">rvm</h4>
<ol>
  <li>rvm -v 查看rvm版本</li>
  <li>rvm list known 列出已知ruby的版本</li>
  <li>rvm install 2.4.0  安装新版本</li>
</ol>
<hr />

<h4 id="gem">Gem</h4>
<p>gem是管理Ruby库和程序的标准包，通过使用Ruby Gem源来查找，安装，升级和卸载软件</p>
<ol>
  <li>gem install [gemname] 从Gem源安装gem包</li>
  <li>gem update            更新所有已安装的gem包</li>
  <li>gem list              查看本机已经安装的所有gem包</li>
</ol>

